The Graphiti Diagram Editor for the Fowler DSL in its very first version. Shows the integration of Xtext and Graphiti to work with the very same model.

<img src="https://github.com/joergreichert/Permet/raw/master/wiki/fowlerDslGraphitiV001.png" alt="Xtext Editor, Graphiti Editor and EEF Properties View" width="1000px" onClick="view();" />

<script language="JavaScript">
function view() {
   imageWindow = window.open("https://github.com/joergreichert/Permet/raw/master/wiki/fowlerDslGraphitiV001.png", 'imageWindow', 'width=600,height=300');    
}
</script>

See also the [Spray](http://code.google.com/a/eclipselabs.org/p/spray/) project, a generator framework for creating domain specific graphical editors.

Navigate back to [overview](http://joergreichert.github.io).
